snippet.title: 3D Fight - Amstrad CPC Gameplay
snippet.description: Developed and published by Loriciels in 1985 exclusively for the Amstrad, there is very little info found around this game, considering it was only ever sold in France. What I do know, however, is that it reminds me of Space Harrier and Zoom 909.
